title: Opie & Jim Norton NOV 02 2015 Mon.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton NOV 02 2015 Mon (03:10:10)

On Today's Show:

BOB SAGET, PETE DAVIDSON, JENNY HUTT.

Bob Saget joins them and he talks about a new Broadway play that he is in until January, his relationship status, a new Full House TV show, they talk about Halloween stuff including needles being found in candy, and Pete Davidson joins them as Bob gets ready to go to TV.

They talk about some football and baseball, Pete tells a story about a football player who was a dick to him, they cover a news story about a sex scandal at Notre Dame, and Pete tells a story involving sending pics of his dick to his mom.

They check out a video of an Uber driver getting beaten up by a drunk rider, they check out video of a woman confronting a guy who was creeping on her, they talk about Tiger Woods' former caddy, and pills in Halloween candy.

Jenny Hutt joins them. They check out video of a guy who got thrown out of his car after it crashed and he landed on a highway sign. Jenny gets abused. They talk about Harry Hamlin getting in trouble over a Halloween costume and they check out some of Jenny's old videos
